&lt;p&gt;
	Cois B&aacute; means Bayside and that is literally where we are located, a stone&#39;s throw from the beach on Dundalk Bay. This newly refurbished cottage has 3 bedrooms, two double, one en suite, one twin, with extra beds available when necessary. There are 2 reception rooms, one with an open fire and one with a gas fire, TV, Video, DVD and Bar. The heart of the house is a charming country kitchen, fully equipped with all mod cons, fridge/freezer, washing machine/dryer, dish washer, microwave, etc. and a traditional Irish dresser.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Cois B&aacute; is a child friendly home with a cot and high chair for the baby and a large safe drive-in back yard for children to play in, while you relax on the patio among the flower pots or enjoy a meal on the gas barbeque. If you would like to go fishing a charter can be arranged.&lt;/p&gt;

