&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; &quot;&gt;
	&lt;font color=&quot;#cc0033&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#009900&quot;&gt;&quot;Quality Assured&quot;.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; &quot;&gt;
	&lt;strong&gt;The refurbished slate, stone and brick buildings have been tastefully converted into stables with associated facilities. Married with ultra modern, state of the art indoor and outdoor arenas and world - class equestrian facilities the centre has been designed with the safety and comfort of both horse and handler in mind. Our qualified, friendly staff and team of wonderful, good natured Irish ponies, cobs and horses will ensure that you enjoy your time on horseback from the minute you arrive.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

