	&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, sans-serif; &quot;&gt;Daily throughout July/August; subject to weather conditions. Contact Tropicana for times.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
