&lt;p&gt;
	&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; &quot;&gt;We are built on the sea wall overlooking the Harbour.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; &quot;&gt;&nbsp;The harbour is the most&nbsp; historic area of Newcastle. Home to many longstanding families, the harbour is still used for small scale commercial fishing. &ldquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; &quot;&gt;Painstakingly and lovingly converted, these traditional stone cottages offer peace and tranquillity for that well earned break. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.iguidecarlingfordmourne.com/WEBFILES/images/mournecottages1.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 262px; height: 255px; &quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; &quot;&gt;Located at foot of the Mournes and near Newcastle town centre. Mourne Cottages is convenient to a wealth of activities including golf, pony trekking, fishing, golden beaches etc. Furnished to a very high standard with private garden and patio. Near Mullough Beach, Tollymore and Castlewellan Forest Parks.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
	&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 12px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; color: rgb(22, 30, 21); font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; &quot;&gt;
	Tory Bush Cottages are located beside Tollymore Forest Park, overlooking the Mourne Mountains in County Down, Northern Ireland, just 4.5 mile outside the seaside resort of Newcastle&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 12px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; color: rgb(22, 30, 21); font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; &quot;&gt;
	Being just 600 meters from the Ulster Way they are ideally situated for hill walks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 12px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; color: rgb(22, 30, 21); font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; &quot;&gt;
	The self catering cottages are built in the &lsquo;Clachan&rsquo; style, of traditional appearance with white-washed walls and slate roofs. Dry stone walls, original gates and pillars give the appearance of a &lsquo;turn-of-the-century&rsquo; Ulster farm yard.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 12px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; color: rgb(22, 30, 21); font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; &quot;&gt;
	They were, however, built using the latest materials and techniques incorporating high degrees of insulation and an efficient central heating system to give summer warmth all year round.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 12px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; color: rgb(22, 30, 21); font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; &quot;&gt;
	&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.torybush.com/wp-content/uploads/home02.png&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(64, 91, 62); &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;alignright size-full wp-image-151&quot; height=&quot;155&quot; src=&quot;http://www.torybush.com/wp-content/uploads/home02.png&quot; style=&quot;border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; float: right; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(192, 208, 190); border-right-color: rgb(192, 208, 190); border-bottom-color: rgb(192, 208, 190); border-left-color: rgb(192, 208, 190); margin-top: 1em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em; &quot; title=&quot;home02&quot; width=&quot;218&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;There is a choice of a 1, 2,3, or even a 4 bedroom cottage, In each cottage there is a main and an en-suite Bathroom. There is a fully fitted kitchen, with a gas hob &amp; electric fan oven. Dual microwave &amp; grill. Dishwasher &amp; washing machine. Fridge freezer.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
